Life on Earth is pretty different for Ax. But there is one thing he, Cassie, Marco, Jake, Rachel, and Tobias have in common. Something that one alien, four kids and a hawk know they have to do...stop the Yeerks...', 'An alien warrior, Ax, joins the Animorphs to fight the Yeerks on Earth, navigating strange human customs and a shared mission.', 1997, '0590997289', '9780590997287', NULL, NULL, 195, 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/385971-L.jpg', '/works/OL27772W', NULL, '1997-06', 'English', NULL, 1, 0, 'the-alien-katherine-applegate', 0, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 'public', '2026-03-18 19:48:38', '2026-03-22 04:09:36');
